      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for practical transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows clear signs of its age, including some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. There are no major mechanical issues, though it may require more frequent maintenance than a newer model. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any frills.",
