      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW\u2019s S54B32 power unit, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp throttle response. Mated to a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, the mechanical synchronization is flawless. The chassis remains structurally impeccable, with a documented rear subframe inspection and reinforcement. Performance is anchored by the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential and a precision-aligned multi-link rear suspension. This specimen is mechanically turn-key, having undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and VANOS overhaul, ensuring its 8,000 RPM redline remains as potent as the day it left Regensburg.",
      "price": 48900.0,
